{"tid":659303,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"蘋果分析師：2019料推三攝iPhone","createTime":"2018-05-09T16:53:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-10T00:09:21.000Z","uid":70274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"7596362619c20d8e51827814820029515f5843d9","tid":659303,"uid":70274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T16:53:57.000Z","msg":"中環街市<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n市場經常以產品來評定企業前途，例如小米快將上市，大家會研究，小米在印度市場的佔有率，到底是否比預期的高？又有人會研究，到底小米做家電的潛力大，抑或生產手機的優勢更好？<br />\n<br />\n股神早前押注蘋果，那麼，蘋果今年又會有什麼新產品呢？踏入第二季，提醒大家又有新iPhone，基本上已是指定動作，剛好這幾天，又有新iPhone傳聞，不妨先睹為快。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今次傳出新iPhone配置的是元大證券（Yuanta Securities）的分析師Jeff Pu，根據他的報告指出，蘋果極有可能今年會將鏡頭升級至三鏡頭。用意很明顯，就是要抗衡華為P20 Pro的三攝功能。<br />\n<br />\n歸納所有傳聞，新iPhone預期將有1,200萬畫素6P防手震規格，並能做到5倍變焦效果，第三個鏡頭則可提供3倍光學變焦功能。<br />\n<br />\n作為果迷的你，又收唔收貨呢？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n的而且確，在手機攝影能力上領先的，早已經不是蘋果；甚至有分析指，華為P20 Pro的攝影能力，已經超越 iPhone X和Galaxy S9。因此，若然今年蘋果驚喜欠奉，隨時連股神都要「蝕桌」。<br />\n<br />\n天下大勢，向來以蘋果、三星獨領風騷，近年中國品牌彈起。國產機遇上美國的封殺行動，似乎只是前奏，且看今年「神之手機」，會否給國產手機，帶來更正面的致命一擊。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/finance/蘋果分析師-2019料推三攝iphone-075657340.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.mobi.yahoo.com%2Ffinance%2F%E8%98%8B%E6%9E%9C%E5%88%86%E6%9E%90%E5%B8%AB-2019%E6%96%99%E6%8E%A8%E4%B8%89%E6%94%9Diphone-075657340.html&d=hqf1htzJ1Ga3w0DgU5664DCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=c5909d91\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.mobi.yahoo.com/finance/蘋果分析師-2019料推三攝iphone-075657340.html</a>"},{"pid":"69a8add2312d89571cf1f295f0203e04559294bf","tid":659303,"uid":144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T16:56:51.000Z","msg":"幾時出四cam 五cam 六cam<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"285ce2da49d61c5705feacae93ac90f0ebfd37bc","tid":659303,"uid":45368,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"69a8add2312d89571cf1f295f0203e04559294bf","tid":659303,"uid":144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T16:56:51.000Z","msg":"幾時出四cam 五cam 六cam<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T22:24:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/10/062403_e798c0e01899800b42a0ca5f9a927484.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F10%2F062403_e798c0e01899800b42a0ca5f9a927484.png&h=718aa93b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f8c45485c2bb0a9d9144570f1d374c323b8d6fc9","tid":659303,"uid":52595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T23:17:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6e01e85127c363afcbee57f398d23f35e335b22b","tid":659303,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T23:20:34.000Z","msg":"多鏡頭有咩好？"},{"pid":"4c298c51c85e9b634d95245b9a65d093c53f5546","tid":659303,"uid":55851,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T23:33:50.000Z","msg":"三鏡就三鏡，三乜撚野攝"},{"pid":"1d268c6a2b100ee1c751b57678865a5b439a9d6a","tid":659303,"uid":29703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T23:36:59.000Z","msg":"曲線幫小米華為做廣告咁 咩抗衡華為？ 人地都無放過你係眼內"},{"pid":"47bf255e9fb828679e4136d7e83c2ac69da70b8e","tid":659303,"uid":5178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d268c6a2b100ee1c751b57678865a5b439a9d6a","tid":659303,"uid":29703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T23:36:59.000Z","msg":"曲線幫小米華為做廣告咁 咩抗衡華為？ 人地都無放過你係眼內"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T00:06:21.000Z","msg":"財演鬼識咩 左抄右抄<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d55bf0594d64bf9c27660e05da3378eb4068ea58","tid":659303,"uid":77134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-10T00:09:21.000Z","msg":"抄p20?"}]}